# Iteration 1 Project Board

## Objective

The objective of Iteration 1 is to review the planned user stories for Milestone 1 and implement the first group of high-priority user stories.

In this iteration, the team will focus on the basic user account system and the first reading progress feature. These functions are important because they provide the foundation for later features such as reading clubs, comments, bookmarks, notifications, and theme switching.

## Selected User Stories for Iteration 1

| User Story                                                                    | Priority | Estimated Effort | Status |
| ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- | -------: | ---------------: | ------ |
| As a user, I want to create an account so that I can save my reading progress |       10 |           2 days | Todo   |
| As a user, I want to log in securely so that my data is protected             |       10 |           2 days | Todo   |
| As a user, I want to create reading goals so that I can track my progress     |       20 |           3 days | Todo   |

## Project Board Columns

The project board uses the following columns:

| Column      | Description                                       |
| ----------- | ------------------------------------------------- |
| Todo        | User stories that are planned but not started yet |
| In Progress | User stories that are currently being implemented |
| Done        | User stories that have been completed and tested  |

