## Reason for Selecting These User Stories

The account creation and secure login user stories are selected because they have the highest priority and are required for user-based features. Without an account system, users cannot save personal reading progress or manage their own data.

The reading goal feature is also selected because it is directly related to the main purpose of the Read! Reading Management System. It allows users to set goals and begin tracking their reading progress.

## Expected Outcome

By the end of Iteration 1, the team aims to complete at least two user stories:

1. Account creation
2. Secure login

If time allows, the team will also start or complete the reading goal feature.
